By accessing this database and using this information, you acknowledge your understanding and compliance to the above.You further agree that you have a "legitimate interest" to access this data provided here and that it will be used only for the purpose intended/meant for standardization of the estimation process. This information must not be shared or discussed with third parties or anyone inside or outside of IBM other than those who have a business need for the information and subject to appropriate confidentiality agreements. It must also be consistent with country specific rules applicable for certain types of data (e.g. works agreements) and handled securely, in accordance with applicable IBM security documentation.

monthlyL1TicketsAssumed.text: Calculated roughly as 70% of the total tickets. This is just to give an idea of L1 tickets the system could be generating. This value is not used in this estimation.

l1DistributionPercentage.label: L1.5 + Small SRs percentage
l1DistributionPercentage.text: L1.5 tickets: Simple resolutions / repeatable solutions . Small SR's: 0.5 to 2 Hours. Input taken from reference sheet. Based on Technology distribution.

l2DistributionPercentage.label: L2 + Medium SRs percentage
l2DistributionPercentage.text: L2 Tickets: Configuration changes / really simple visual changes. Medium SR's: 2 to 6 Hours.Input taken from reference sheet. Based on Technology distribution.

l3DistributionPercentage.label: L3 + Large SRs percentage
l3DistributionPercentage.text: L3 tickets: minor code changes / compex configurations / reports / etc. Large SR's: 6 to 14 Hours.Input taken from reference sheet. Based on Technology distribution.

l4DistributionPercentage.label: L4 percentage
l4DistributionPercentage.text: L4 Tickets: Time taken to work with 3rd party vendor tickets /cots vendors. Input taken from reference sheet. Based on Technology distribution.

minorEnhDistributionPercentage.label: Minor Enhnacements + V.Large SRs percentage
minorEnhDistributionPercentage.text: Minor code changes which donâ€™t take more 3 - 5 person days. Average 40 hrs. V.Large SR's: 14 Hours to 40 Hours.

minorEnhTicketsCountDistribution.label: Count of Minor Enhancement tickets
minorEnhTicketsCountDistribution.text: Assuming 25% of the minor enhancement releases will be external facing web applications

additionalADCapacityHrsDistributionPerce.label: Additional AD Capacity Hours Requested Monthly(optional)
additionalADCapacityHrsDistributionPerce.text: Add total hours as required by the Client for capacity related requirements (Eg.: AD Capacity, Reporting, etc.).Look over the distribution across S, M & C.
additionalADCapacityHrsDistributionPerce.errorText: Please add correct capacity of hours in colF of this row

additionalADCapacityHrsDistribution.label: AD Capacity Distribution
additionalADCapacityHrsDistribution.text: Distribution of total capacity of hours should be 100% across S, M & C application group
